Skills.Name: Inevitable Sword Zone
Skills.Description: Grants 2x <code=200,param=1001><color=#3398f1>Parry</color> on self for 15s. Inflicts <code=400,param=208><color=#3398f1>Provoke</color> on all enemies for 15s. Further lowers ATK by <color=red>{4}%</color> multiplied by number of Elves in party for 15s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Grants Parry on self. Inflicts Provoke on all enemies, lowers ATK based on number of Elves in party

Skills.Name: Fleeting Swordplay
Skills.Description: Inflicts 3-hit DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> + <color=red>{1}%</color> + <color=red>{2}%</color>) on single enemy. Further raises DMG Received by <color=red>{3}%</color> for 10s if Green Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts 3-hit DMG on single enemy, raises DMG Received if Green Elemental

Skills.Name: Hero's Sword Flash
Skills.Description: Inflicts 2-hit DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> + <color=red>{1}%</color>) on single enemy. Recovers own HP by {2}% of ATK. Further grants 3x <code=200,param=1001><color=#3398f1>Parry</color> for 15s. Recovers SP of all Red Elemental allies (except self) by {7} multiplied by number of Elves in party. Further recovers SP by 20.00 if Elf.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts 2-hit DMG on single enemy. Recovers own HP, grants Parry. Recovers SP of all Red Elemental allies (except self) based on number of Elves in party, recovers SP if Elf

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Reduces DMG Received for all allies by <color=red>5.00%-40.00%</color> for 5s according to Combo Bonus. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription: Reduces DMG Received for all allies. Inflicts DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Genesis Paladin
Skills.Description: At start of Wave, raises own DEF by <color=red>{1}%</color> multiplied by number of Elves in party for 60s. <code=200,param=115><color=#3398f1>Shields</color> DMG ({3}% of skill user's ATK) of all Red Elemental allies (behind self) for 30s.
Skills.ShortDescription: At start of Wave, raises own DEF based on number of Elves in party. Shields DMG of all Red Elemental allies (behind self)
